  "subject": "[feeder] 1.2.0 release",
  "commit_message": "[feeder] 1.2.0 release\n\n- migrate from DMaaP message-router to direct Kafka (AdminClient)\n- move Kafka connection config from database to application.properties\n- make SASL mechanism and JAAS config configurable via environment variables\n- upgrade Spring Boot 2.1.0 → 2.7.18 and all major dependencies\n  (kafka-clients 3.3.2, postgresql 42.6.0, MongoDB driver 4.9.1, ES 7.17.14)\n- replace deprecated Springfox with SpringDoc OpenAPI 1.7.0\n- extract DataSource bean into dedicated configuration class\n- add SpringBootTest context smoke test to catch startup regressions in CI\n- make JVM MaxRAMPercentage configurable in Dockerfile (default 75 %)\n\nIssue-ID: DCAEGEN2-3444\nChange-Id: I24f92abefad7be676c0404cef6ba5b6c6e8321e7\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
